s://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54183779836_fa47b53795_h.jpg\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn the camp, the seasonal BGM ‘Dawn (Winter)’ and ‘Take me away’ create a relaxing atmosphere. These romantic tunes will enhance your holiday relaxation by melting away battle tension.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eA surprise gift from Santa\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54182900157_b7e454333b_h.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54182900157_b7e454333b_h.jpg\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA new mini-game has arrived in Xion, offering a break from survival struggles. Enjoy the gameplay and earn rewards upon completion.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Santa Dress for Eve is designed as an adorable and festive appearance. The I’m No Santa costume for Adam has a humorous twist. Complete the look with the Santa Girl hairstyle and personalize it with accessories such as Snow Crystal Glasses, Wreath Earrings, and Sleigh Ear Cuffs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"399670\" src=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=1 2560w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.75 1920w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.57 1459w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.46 1178w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.37 947w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.31 794w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.24 614w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/23a86ffdf488f73980b7f2526039d06208feaa11-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.19 486w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1170px) 936px, (min-width: 960px) 80vw, 100vw\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"399673\" src=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b663eccc0d1b907-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b663eccc0d1b907-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=1 2560w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b663eccc0d1b907-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.75 1920w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b663eccc0d1b907-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.57 1459w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b663eccc0d1b907-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.46 1178w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b663eccc0d1b907-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.37 947w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b663eccc0d1b907-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.31 794w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b663eccc0d1b907-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.24 614w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/fdfccb1b3f525bc7d7ad14192b6