cbd40f411-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=1 2560w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/78fdfc6771ad228d5b0d7641678ea4acbd40f411-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.75 1920w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/78fdfc6771ad228d5b0d7641678ea4acbd40f411-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.57 1459w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/78fdfc6771ad228d5b0d7641678ea4acbd40f411-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.46 1178w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/78fdfc6771ad228d5b0d7641678ea4acbd40f411-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.37 947w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/78fdfc6771ad228d5b0d7641678ea4acbd40f411-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.31 794w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/78fdfc6771ad228d5b0d7641678ea4acbd40f411-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.24 614w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/78fdfc6771ad228d5b0d7641678ea4acbd40f411-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.19 486w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1170px) 936px, (min-width: 960px) 80vw, 100vw\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"399671\" src=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=1 2560w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.75 1920w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.57 1459w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.46 1178w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.37 947w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.31 794w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.24 614w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2024/12/3e0fcdc9a2d7aab218c39d0ff2532c37bd2fb44a-scaled.jpg?resize=2560%2C1440\u0026amp;zoom=0.19 486w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1170px) 936px, (min-width: 960px) 80vw, 100vw\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe newly added Rudolph Pack cosmetic for the Drone is an endearing item reimagining Rudolph leading Santa’s sleigh.  With a red nose and cute horns, this Drone is sure to brighten up your holiday.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54183798571_a983253597_h.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54183798571_a983253597_h.jpg\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSet the season as you please\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOn/Off feature has been newly added for the seasonal events and NieR:Automata DLC content. You can now enjoy the game whenever and however you want.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54183798561_cf2a663e4e_h.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54183798561_cf2a663e4e_h.jpg\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAlways with a heart full of gratitude\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eCreate unforgettable memories with these gifts prepared in Stellar Blade this cold winter. The dev team put extra touch to this update to deliver a joyful holiday to all. May the streets of Xion that were once cold, and empty be filled with the wonders of the season.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe strive to bring joy to your life. Have a warm and happy holidays with Stellar Blade!\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/article\u003e\u003csection\u003e\n\t\u003ch2\u003eTrending Stories\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\t\n\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
